{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/,_N_T_/index"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/__PAGE__","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/destinations/palawan.svg\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/39mx9nov1com1.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/40e0f9pufs6g4.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/27jktro2p5rq9.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3peubv2924kx4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07u_h6i539_wj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0tv_qyohsmak0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3ryatpyrium8c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/35k6dddhtu1t7.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#0F766E\"/><title>TravelDesk</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Branded booking and operations software for travel businesses.\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.webmanifest\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"default\"/><meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.svg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-icon-180.png\" sizes=\"180x180\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><main class=\"td-page\"><header class=\"td-header\"><div class=\"td-container td-nav\"><a class=\"logo \" href=\"/\"><span class=\"logo-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i></i><i></i><i></i></span><span>TravelDesk</span></a><nav class=\"td-nav-links\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\"><a href=\"#platform\">Platform</a><a href=\"#how-it-works\">How it works</a><a href=\"#business\">For agencies</a><a href=\"/login\">Sign in</a><a class=\"td-nav-cta\" href=\"/register\">Start now</a></nav></div></header><section class=\"td-hero\"><div class=\"td-container td-hero-grid\"><div class=\"td-hero-copy\"><span class=\"td-overline\">Booking software for Philippine travel businesses</span><h1>Run your travel business from one desk.</h1><p>TravelDesk gives your customers a proper place to search and book, while your team manages availability, payments, and travelers behind the scenes.</p><div class=\"td-actions\"><a class=\"td-button td-button-primary\" href=\"/register\">Build your booking site <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"td-button td-button-secondary\" href=\"/demo-travel\">View customer demo</a></div><div class=\"td-hero-trust\"><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> Secure booking flow</span><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> Your own brand</span></div></div><div class=\"td-hero-media\"><img alt=\"A tropical Palawan destination\" width=\"760\" height=\"560\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/destinations/palawan.svg\"/><div class=\"td-booking-board\"><span class=\"td-board-label\">NEXT DEPARTURE</span><strong>El Nido Island Escape</strong><div class=\"td-board-route\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plane\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17.8 19.2 16 11l3.5-3.5C21 6 21.5 4 21 3c-1-.5-3 0-4.5 1.5L13 8 4.8 6.2c-.5-.1-.9.1-1.1.5l-.3.5c-.2.5-.1 1 .3 1.3L9 12l-2 3H4l-1 1 3 2 2 3 1-1v-3l3-2 3.5 5.3c.3.4.8.5 1.3.3l.5-.2c.4-.3.6-.7.5-1.2z\"></path></svg> Manila <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg> El Nido</div><div class=\"td-board-meta\"><span><b>18 Jul</b><small>Departure</small></span><span><b>12 / 14</b><small>Travelers paid</small></span></div></div><div class=\"td-confirmed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Booking confirmed</div></div></div></section><section class=\"td-proof-bar\"><div class=\"td-container\"><span>Built for independent operators</span><strong>Branded website</strong><strong>Customer booking app</strong><strong>Admin workspace</strong><strong>Philippine peso ready</strong></div></section><section id=\"platform\" class=\"td-services\"><div class=\"td-container\"><div class=\"td-section-heading\"><span>WHAT TRAVELDESK DOES</span><h2>Less manual follow-up. More confirmed bookings.</h2><p>One connected system for the customer experience and the work your team does every day.</p></div><div class=\"td-service-grid\"><article class=\"td-service-item\"><div class=\"td-service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h3>Search and booking</h3><p>Let customers check tours and flights, choose dates, and book without waiting for a reply.</p></article><article class=\"td-service-item\"><div class=\"td-service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3>Live availability</h3><p>Keep seats, departures, appointments, and booking cutoffs accurate in one calendar.</p></article><article class=\"td-service-item\"><div class=\"td-service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><h3>Business operations</h3><p>Manage payments, travelers, staff activity, and daily sales from one practical workspace.</p></article></div></div></section><section id=\"business\" class=\"td-split-section\"><div class=\"td-container td-split-grid\"><div class=\"td-destination-panel\"><img alt=\"Cebu travel destination\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"720\" height=\"620\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/destinations/cebu.svg\"/><div class=\"td-sales-card\"><span>BOOKINGS THIS MONTH</span><strong>128</strong><small>18% higher than last month</small></div></div><div class=\"td-split-copy\"><span class=\"td-overline\">Made for real agency work</span><h2>Stop running the business through chat threads.</h2><p>Inquiries can still start on Messenger or Viber. The actual booking should move into a system your staff and customers can trust.</p><ul><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Availability is checked before a customer pays.</li><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Every booking has one clear status and payment record.</li><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Staff work from the same customer and departure data.</li><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg> Customers receive a consistent, branded experience.</li></ul><a class=\"td-text-link\" href=\"/demo-dashboard\">See the business dashboard <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"td-process\"><div class=\"td-container\"><div class=\"td-section-heading td-section-heading-left\"><span>HOW IT WORKS</span><h2>From setup to your first online booking.</h2></div><div class=\"td-step-grid\"><article><span>01</span><h3>Set up your business</h3><p>Add your brand, services, schedules, payment rules, and staff.</p></article><article><span>02</span><h3>Publish your booking site</h3><p>Give customers a professional website they can also install as an app.</p></article><article><span>03</span><h3>Run everything in one place</h3><p>Confirm bookings, track payments, and keep customers updated.</p></article></div></div></section><section class=\"td-support-band\"><div class=\"td-container\"><div><span class=\"td-support-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg></span><div><strong>You are not buying software and figuring it out alone.</strong><p>TravelDesk onboarding helps your team set up services, schedules, and booking rules correctly.</p></div></div><div class=\"td-support-stats\"><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg><b>Team onboarding</b></span><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><b>Operational safeguards</b></span></div></div></section><section class=\"td-final-cta\"><div class=\"td-container\"><div><span>READY TO OPERATE PROFESSIONALLY?</span><h2>Give customers confidence before they send a payment.</h2></div><a class=\"td-button td-button-orange\" href=\"/register\">Start building <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"luc